Meet Mallory

Everyone is deserving of help and being heard. Through web development, it is my mission to use my passion for creating solutions to help clients provide the best resources to the communities they serve. I choose to be a web developer because I want to lead by example to inspire the younger generation of women in STEM and to foster diverse-thinkers. I believe that persistence is key and that the journey is just as important as the end result.

Here are a few technologies I've been working with recently:

  • JavaScript
  • Next.js
  • React
  • Typescript
  • Html
